# Privacy Policy

## Introduction
This privacy policy explains how our browser extension processes and handles data. The extension is designed to modify certain page elements and add affiliate/referral codes to links on specific websites.

## Data Collection and Usage
Our extension collects and processes the following limited data:

### Web Browsing History
- **What we collect**: Our extension only detects when you visit specific websites where our functionality is needed.
- **How we use it**: This information is used solely to activate the extension's functionality on relevant pages.
- **Data storage**: This information is processed in real-time and is not stored or transmitted to external servers.

### Website Content
- **What we access**: Our extension accesses the content of websites you visit where our extension is active.
- **How we use it**: This access is solely for the purpose of:
  1. Removing certain error messages or annoying elements from the page
  2. Modifying links to include our affiliate/referral codes
- **Data storage**: Content is only processed locally in your browser and is not stored or transmitted to external servers.

## No Personal Data Collection
Our extension does NOT collect:
- Personal information (names, email addresses, etc.)
- Health information
- Financial information
- Authentication data
- Personal communications
- Location data
- User activity beyond what's necessary for the extension's core functionality

## Data Sharing
We do not share any user data with third parties. The sole purpose of this extension is to add affiliate/referral codes to links, which benefits the developer while providing a better browsing experience for users by removing annoying elements.

## Affiliate/Referral Disclosure
When you click on modified links, we may earn a commission from resulting purchases or actions. This comes at no additional cost to you and does not affect the prices of products or services.

## Changes to This Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify users of any significant changes through the extension update process.

## Contact Information
If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at: elitereps218@gmail.com

